"QuALM" is a cue advancer for Live MIDI.

## Building

Requires Java 8+ and [Gradle](https://gradle.org/) (or use the system Ant if
you prefer the legacy build).

```
# compile
gradle build

# run all tests
gradle test

# build a runnable jar
gradle jar
```

The jar lands at `build/libs/qualm.jar`. Run it with:

```
java -jar build/libs/qualm.jar <control-file.xml>
```

## Data Format

Control files are written in XML (see `doc/README` for the original format
description) or in the newer YAML format (see `doc/parser-rewrite/YAML_SPEC.md`).

## Upcoming Format Migration

The project is in the process of migrating its data format from XML to a
leaner YAML representation. See `doc/parser-rewrite/PLAN.md` for the full
project plan and `doc/parser-rewrite/YAML_SPEC.md` for the new YAML schema.

